\begin_body

\begin_layout Chapter*
\begin_inset Newpage newpage
\end_inset

Abstract
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size small
In this Final Degree Project we deal with the design of a bot (or AI) for
 RTS games using evolutionary techniques, specifically genetic algorithms.
 As environment for testing our design techniques will be used a game proposed
 int the Google AI Challenge called Planet Wars.
 Therefore, the rules and concept of the game will be presented.
 First an initial design to the bot using an reactive AI is presented.
 Then, this AI is optimized using a genetic algorithm.
 Studies for this algorithm have been performed to verify that decisions
 made are correct and extrapolated to other similar design problems.
 Both studies are presented: related to software performance, and studies
 focus on the fitness quality and concept.
 The fitness is the key to determine the quality of our AI design.
 Finally, we present a design method specialist and adaptive, using to create
 it the optimization mechanism provided by the genetic algorithm.
\end_layout

